    "During self-supervised pretraining, random patches are masked before all of the patches are passed to a transformer encoder.",
    "The model is trained to jointly reconstruct the masked audio and to classify the order of which the masked audio occurs.",
    "The transformer is made up of 12 multihead attention blocks.",
    "The model is trained end to end, with gradients being passed all of the way back to the convolutional feature extractors.",
    "The model is pre-trained on a combined set of AudioSet-2M (ref."
